definitions.definition: Debased , corrupt ; seeking personal gain by dishonourable means.
Taking part in promiscuous sexual activity, licentious ; ( later, chiefly as attributive use of noun ) that is a prostitute.

main_definition: ( obsolete ) Debased , corrupt ; seeking personal gain by dishonourable means. [16th–19th c.]
secondary_definitions: Taking part in promiscuous sexual activity, licentious ; ( later, chiefly as attributive use of noun ) that is a prostitute. [from 16th c.]
( obsolete ) Exposed , subjected ( to something shameful). [16th–18th c.]
